Package: remotecontrol
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
	${misc:Depends}
Description: Controller for building automation devices
 GNU remotecontrol is a web application serving as a management tool for
 (possibly multiple) IP-enabled HVAC thermostats and other Building
 Automation devices. 
